FreePiano 2.1
; keypiano default keymap — QWERTY, two chromatic octaves (C3–B4)
; White keys: Z-M row (octave 3, left hand), Y-] row (octave 4, right hand)
; Black keys sit ABOVE the gap between their two white keys, matching a real
;   piano: C#=S (between Z/X), D#=D, F#=G, G#=H, A#=J        (octave 3)
;          C#=7 (between Y/U), D#=8, F#=0, G#=-, A#==        (octave 4)
; F1/F2 = octave down/up
; Pedals (hold like a real piano pedal): Space = sustain (damper),
;   F3 = sostenuto, F4 = soft (una corda)

; ── Octave 3 – white keys (Z row, left hand) ─────────────────────────────────
Keydown Z Note In_0 C3
Label Z Z
Keydown X Note In_0 D3
Label X X
Keydown C Note In_0 E3
Label C C
Keydown V Note In_0 F3
Label V V
Keydown B Note In_0 G3
Label B B
Keydown N Note In_0 A3
Label N N
Keydown M Note In_0 B3
Label M M

; ── Octave 3 – black keys (home row, above the gap between white keys) ───────
Keydown S Note In_0 C#3
Label S S
Keydown D Note In_0 Eb3
Label D D
Keydown G Note In_0 F#3
Label G G
Keydown H Note In_0 Ab3
Label H H
Keydown J Note In_0 Bb3
Label J J

; ── Octave 4 – white keys (Y row, right hand) ────────────────────────────────
Keydown Y Note In_0 C4
Label Y Y
Keydown U Note In_0 D4
Label U U
Keydown I Note In_0 E4
Label I I
Keydown O Note In_0 F4
Label O O
Keydown P Note In_0 G4
Label P P
Keydown LBracket Note In_0 A4
Label LBracket [
Keydown RBracket Note In_0 B4
Label RBracket ]

; ── Octave 4 – black keys (number row, above the gap between white keys) ──────
Keydown 7 Note In_0 C#4
Label 7 7
Keydown 8 Note In_0 Eb4
Label 8 8
Keydown 0 Note In_0 F#4
Label 0 0
Keydown Minus Note In_0 Ab4
Label Minus -
Keydown Equals Note In_0 Bb4
Label Equals =

; ── Controls ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Keydown F1 Octave In_0 Dec 1
Label F1 Oct-
Keydown F2 Octave In_0 Inc 1
Label F2 Oct+
Keydown Space SustainPedal In_0
Label Space Sus
Keydown F3 Sostenuto In_0
Label F3 Sost
Keydown F4 Soft In_0
Label F4 Soft
